1. Two players start the game.they place their pieces on the first
   square of the board.
2. The game decides which one is the current player.
3. Current player rolls a die.
4. Current player moves his piece by the value of die face.
5. If the piece lands on snake or ladder , set the piece position 
   to the opposite end of the snake/ladder.
6. If the piece lands on the goal square, then the current player 
   win, else change the current player then repeat step (3.)